              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-red-900 mb-2">Don't Wait Until After a Flood</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-red-800 leading-relaxed">
                  Post-flood repairs are 2-3x more expensive than preventative solutions because you're paying for damage remediation
                  (contents, drywall, flooring, mold) PLUS the waterproofing work. Insurance may not cover you, especially for
                  repeated claims. Act now while your basement is dry.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
